&lt;p&gt;å®˜æ–¹å‚è€ƒæ–‡æ¡£ï¼š&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9jaXJjbGVjaS5jb20vZG9jcy8yLjAvY29uZmlndXJhdGlvbi1yZWZlcmVuY2UvI3ZlcnNpb24=&#34;&gt;https://circleci.com/docs/2.0/configuration-reference/#version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
